The '''''Malka'an Eternal''''' was an enormous pleasure cruiser, which crashed on [[Edonaaris]] after its crew was forced to abandon it, leaving behind all its [[Droid/Legends|droids]]. It was later found by a crew of [[Human/Legends|Human]] scavengers who were killed by the surviving maintenance droid [[SCr-114]], who in turn stole their [[Starship/Legends|ship]].<ref name="SOR">{{JournalCite|5|Smugglers of the Outer Rim}}</ref>

